content: This reeeally has potential to be the single BEST Hex plugin available. However, theres a few issues that are really annoying. First, in the extra preferences, there are 2 different boxes both for "QS tile" (selectable choices) and the other for "QS toggle" (enable/disable checkbox). Really confusing. Next, there is no longer an option to change the "settings" system app icons (or my files, gallery, etc.) and the setting was available previously. Reeeally want to use this theme properly...
Love the theme! Thank you dev for answering my questions!
